emented projects.\r\n\r\nTo send your contribution you can use PayPal by clicking on the \"Donate\" button below.   Alternatively you can send a personal check - to arrange this please send an e-mail through the Contact Us page.\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Your contribution is greatly appreciated by the Handmaids of the Blessed Trinity and betters the lives of the orphans under their care.</strong></span>\r\n\r\n<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_blank\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"cmd\" value=\"_s-xclick\" />\r\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"hosted_button_id\" value=\"BGG3VL42SCA5L\" />\r\n<input type=\"image\" alt=\"PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!\" name=\"submit\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/btn/btn_donateCC_LG.gif\" />\r\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_US/i/scr/pixel.gif\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /></form>','Support Us','','inherit','open','open','','11-revision-v1','','','2014-03-26 03:23:43','2014-03-26 03:23:43','',11,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/uncategorized/11-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(585,1,'2014-03-26 03:24:48','2014-03-26 03:24:48','<span style=\"line-height: 1.5em;\">The HMBT order relies entirely on receiving outside donations and generating of funds from within.  There is no steady stream of funding coming from any parent organization.   The HMBT is registered as an Indian NGO under the secular name Sneha Jewan Kendra which means Love and Life Center.  Effort is currently underway to register Sneha Jewan Kendra in the United States as a charitable 501 C 3 organization.  </span>\r\n\r\nOn the left sidebar of this page you can see a list of the major current needs at the orphanages.   You will also see examples of recently funded and implemented projects.\r\n\r\nTo send your contribution you can use PayPal by clicking on the \"Donate\" button below.   Alternatively you can send a pers