phanges.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/DSC01230-Mobile.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-537\" alt=\"DSC01230 (Mobile)\" src=\"http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/DSC01230-Mobile.jpg\" width=\"427\" height=\"320\" /></a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The coding &amp; programming of this website was done by the following students at the Eastern Michigan University as a class project:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"> Matthew Juntunen,  Vitaly Peker,  Michael Taulbee,  Lei Qian,  Bhakti Wakchaure</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The map art on the locations page was done by:   Allison Hoff</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>','About this Website','','inherit','open','open','','491-revision-v1','','','2014-04-11 13:31:39','2014-04-11 13:31:39','',491,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/uncategorized/491-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(825,1,'2014-04-11 13:31:59','2014-04-11 13:31:59','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The text, photos, and general layout themes of this website were created and supplied by  Jayesh Shah.   He is an Emergency Medicine physician living in Ann Arbor,  Michigan,  U.S.A.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">He is the current website administrator and the United States contact for these Orphanges.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/DSC01230-Mobile.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-537\" alt=\"DSC01230 (Mobile)\" src=\"http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/DSC01230-Mobile.jpg\" width=\"427\" height=\"320\" /></a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The coding &amp; programming of this website was done by the following students at the Eastern Michigan University as a class project:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"> Matthew Juntunen,  Vitaly Peker,  Michael Taulbee,  Lei Qian,  Bhakti Wakchaure</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The map art on the locations page was done by:   Allison Hoff</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>','About this Website','','inherit','open','open','','491-revision-v1','','','2014-04-11 13:31:59','2014-04-11 13:31:59','',491,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/uncategorized/491-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(826,1,'2014-04-11 13:32:28','2014-04-11 13:32:28','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The text, photos, and general layout themes of this website were created and supplied by Jayesh Shah.  He is an Emergency Medicine physician living in Ann Arbor, Michigan,  U.S.A.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">He is the current website administrator and the United States contact for these Orphanges.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/DSC01230-Mobile.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-537\" alt=\"DSC01230 (Mobile)\" src=\"http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/DSC01230-Mobile.jpg\" width=\"427\" height=\"320\" /></a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The coding &amp; programming of this website was done by the following students at the Eastern Michigan University as a class project:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"> Matthew Juntunen,  Vitaly Peker,  Michael Taulbee,  Lei Qian,  Bhakti Wakchaure</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The map art on the locations page was done by:   Allison Hoff</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>','About this Website','','inherit','open','open','','491-revision-v1','','','2014-04-11 13:32:28','2014-04-11 13:32:28','',491,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/uncategorized/491-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(827,1,'2014-04-11 13:32:55','2014-04-11 13:32:55','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The text, photos, and general layout themes of this website were created and supplied by Jayesh Shah.  He is an Emergency Medicine physician living in Ann Arbor, Michigan, U.S.A.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">He is the current website administrator and the United States contact for these Orphanges.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/DSC01230-Mobile.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-537\" alt=\"DSC01230 (Mobile)\" src=\"http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/DSC01230-Mobile.jpg\" width=\"427\" height=\"320\" /></a></p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The coding &amp; programming of this website was done by the following students at the Eastern Michigan University as a class project:</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"> Matthew Juntunen,  Vitaly Peker,  Michael Taulbee,  Lei Qian,  Bhakti Wakchaure</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The map art on the locations page was done by:   Allison Hoff</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>','About this Website','','inherit','open','open','','491-revision-v1','','','2014-04-11 13:32:55','2014-04-11 13:32:55','',491,'http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/uncategorized/491-revision-v1',0,'revision','',0),(828,1,'2014-04-11 13:33:27','2014-04-11 13:33:27','<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The text, photos, and general layout themes of this website were created and supplied by Jayesh Shah.  He is an Emergency Medicine physician living in Ann Arbor, Michigan, U.S.A.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">He is the current website administrator and the United States contact for these Orphanges.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/DSC01230-Mobile.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-537\" alt=\"DSC01230 (Mobile)\" src=\"http://www.vitalypeker.com/handmaids/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/DSC01230-Mobile.jpg\" width=\"427\" height=\"320\" /></a><